x represents an arb int

Interface:
- command line (using list of lists), like tic tac toe
- Kivy
- Pygame

Bud:
- Basic attributes
    - food level
    - speed
    - colony (colour)
- Basic methods
    - eat (when food particle at distance x)
    - duplication (at x food level)
    - death (at x food level)
    - Movement
        - Constant velocity in a direction
            - bounce off walls like pong
            - bounce off other Buds 
- Advanced methods  
    - 


Environment
    - Basic attributes
        - max num food particles
        - list of Buds in environment
    - Basic Methods
        - generate food (when less than max num food particles)
        - Add Buds to list of buds